|last=Vats
|publisher=CNN-IBN
|accessdate=30 March 2012
|date=24 February 2012
}}</ref> ''[[Mumbai Mirror]]'' rated the album with 3 stars out of 5.<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-02-29/music-reviews/31110240_1_vishal-shekhar-special-appearance-guitars
|title=''Kahaani'' music review
|newspaper=The Times of India
|author=[[Mumbai Mirror]]
|accessdate=15 May 2012
|date=29 February 2012
}}</ref> Reviewing the soundtrack for [[Indiatimes]], Anand Vaishnav commented that, "''Kahaani'' as an album, stays honest to the theme of the film."<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://www.indiatimes.com/bollywood/music-review-kahaani-12663.html
