|date=5 March 2012
|location=Calcutta, India
}}</ref> Social-networking website [[Ibibo|Ibibo.com]] developed an online game, ''The Great Indian Parking Wars'', which required players to park Vidya's taxi on a street; it was well-received, reaching 50,000 hits in 10 days.<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/and-more/vidya-balan-s-kahaani-hit-among-online-gamers_107968.htm
|title=Vidya Balan's ''Kahaani'' hit among online gamers
|publisher=Zee News
|agency=IANS
|accessdate=21 March 2012
