}}</ref>

[[File:Vidya Balan at success bash of 'Kahaani'.jpg|thumb|Balan (centre) and Chatterjee (to her left) celebrate the success of ''Kahaani''.|alt=Actress Vidya Balan cuts a cake celebrating the success of ''Kahaani'' while actor Parambrata Chatterjee watches, along with several others.]]
On 5 March 2012, prior to release, [[Kolkata Metro]] authorities objected to a scene in which Balan is pushed by a man onto the tracks as a train arrives. They requested that the scene be removed, as it would remind people of the past suicides, which had tarnished the railway's image.<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/kahaani-s-dream-kolkata-metro-s-nightmare_107035.htm
|title=''Kahaani's'' dream, Kolkata metro's nightmare
|publisher=Zee News
|agency=IANS
|accessdate=21 March 2012
|date=5 March 2012
}}</ref> The filmmakers screened the scene for the authorities and explained that nothing in the film would affect the image of the Metro or prompt people to commit suicide. Convinced, the officials withdrew their objections, and the scene was retained, although it was removed from trailers.<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/movies/metro-clears-vidya-s-scene-in-kahaani_107083.htm
|title=Metro clears Vidya's scene in ''Kahaani''
|publisher=Zee News
|agency=PTI
|accessdate=21 March 2012
|date=5 March 2012
}}</ref>

''Kahaani'' was released on 9 March 2012, a day after [[International Women's Day]].<ref name=Motherhood@ZN>{{cite news
|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity/vidya-s-kahaani-a-celebration-of-womanhood_107271.htm
|title=Vidya's ''Kahaani'': a celebration of womanhood
|publisher=Zee News
|accessdate=2 April 2012
|date=8 March 2012
}}</ref> It played on 1100 screens worldwide.<ref name=75crore@IBN /> CNN-IBN reported that although ''Kahaani'' was ready before ''The Dirty Picture'', distributors deferred its release, fearing that Balan's role of a sexy siren (in ''The Dirty Picture'') after that of a pregnant woman might not be received well.<ref name="ibn rathnam 28march">{{cite web
|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/kahaani-the-mother-of-a-success-story/243546-8-66.html
